            "name_id": 0x53,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Vur."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Umm, the slags here are docile, right?<CR>I didn't mean to intrude."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x223,
            "name_id": 0x53,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Vur! Vur! Vur!<CR>Vur! Vur! Vur!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh? It looks kinda angry...<CR>H-Hold on a second!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc7,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "What really surprised me was that it<CR>just attacked me all of a sudden.<CR>I wonder if I did something wrong..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh right, you need to be quiet in the library. Maybe I was being too loud..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "No. There is no fault to be found in your actions."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, you scared me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Currently, this facility is experiencing malfunctions with several of its operations."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It may cause some inconveniences for the visitors, but we ask for your kind understanding and cooperation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see. This is an old facility. I need to keep my guard up, like when I'm investigating a ruin."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "In addition, bookshelves collapsed the other day, blocking the passage to the lower floor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Ohh, then I guess I can't go any further..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Now, please enjoy the rest of your visit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "(A library where I don't know when I'll get attacked... I guess I won't be able to read a book in peace.)"
        }
    ]
}